name: Thank you.
description:
Given to my top 25 collectors Dec 2021

It has been an intense, crazy, and fun year. So many steps forward that I cannot even count. What I thought just a dying ember has been brought back to life and a flame slowly grows. Thank you everyone for helping to make that happen. Teamwork makes the dream work. Can’t wait to see what 2022 brings!

Wessel ‘21
